OL,3,CNewcastle United appoint Paul Mitchell
OL,4,Cas new Sporting Director
OL,6,FNewcastle United have confirmed the
OL,7,Fappointment of Paul Mitchell as the
OL,8,Fclub's new Sporting Director.
OL,10,FThe 42-year-old replaces Dan Ashworth
OL,11,Fwho has taken up a role with
OL,12,FManchester United after the two clubs
OL,13,Freached a compensation agreement for
OL,14,Fhis immediate release over the weekend.
