OL,3,CNewcastle United appoint Paul Mitchell
OL,4,Cas new Sporting Director
OL,6,FMitchell arrives after previous roles
OL,7,Fin scouting and club development at
OL,8,FSouthampton, Tottenham, RB Leipzig and
OL,9,FMonaco. He has been linked with a host
OL,10,Fof clubs across Europe since his
OL,11,Fdeparture from the Ligue 1 side last
OL,12,Fyear but it is Newcastle who have won
OL,13,Fthe race for his signature.
OL,15,F"It's with immense pride that I accept
OL,16,Fthe responsibility of being Newcastle
OL,17,FUnited's new sporting director," he
OL,18,Fsaid. "I've seen the recent growth and
OL,19,Fambition of the club. This, plus the
OL,20,Famazing fan base, made the decision to
OL,21,Fjoin an easy one.
