OL,3,CNewcastle United appoint Paul Mitchell
OL,4,Cas new Sporting Director
OL,6,FHe became chief scout at MK Dons
OL,7,Fbefore moving to Southampton in 2012.
OL,8,FHe followed manager Mauricio
OL,9,FPochettino to Tottenham in 2014,
OL,10,Fbecoming their head of recruitment.
OL,11,FHis signings for the London club
OL,12,Fincluded Dele Alli and Son Heung-min.
OL,14,FHe later joined the Red Bull group,
OL,15,Fspending time with Leipzig and New
OL,16,FYork before being appointed as Monaco
OL,17,Fsporting director in 2020.
