OL,3,CNewcastle United appoint Paul Mitchell
OL,4,Cas new Sporting Director
OL,6,FDarren Eales, Newcastle United's CEO,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are delighted to welcome
OL,8,FPaul to Newcastle United. He brings a
OL,9,Fsuccessful track record and wealth of
OL,10,Fexperience to the club.
OL,12,F"His extensive and diverse experience
OL,13,Fin football leadership, cultural
OL,14,Fchange and recruitment mean he is the
OL,15,Fideal person to lead our sporting
OL,16,Fdirectorate.
OL,18,F"We look forward to working with Paul
OL,19,Fand supporting him in our pursuit of
OL,20,Flong-term, sustainable success."
